fields.name: Lucent Facial Concentrate
fields.description: A lightweight, fast-absorbing Vitamin C serum that brightens, hydrates, evens skin tone, and boosts radiance.
fields.ingredients: Aqua (Water), Glycerin, Ascorbyl Glucoside, Propanediol, Niacinamide, Sodium Hyaluronate, Panthenol, Camellia Sinensis (Green Tea) Leaf Extract, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Chamomilla Recutita (Chamomile) Flower Extract, Ferulic Acid, Tocopherol, Butylene Glycol, Xanthan Gum, Citric Acid, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin
fields.usage: Apply 2û3 drops to clean, dry skin in the morning and/or evening. Gently pat or massage until fully absorbed. Follow with a moisturiser. During daytime use, apply sunscreen as the final step. Suitable for daily use and for all skin types.

fields.name: Cellular Hyaluronic Moisturizer
fields.description: A hydrating night cream with hyaluronic acid and vitamin E for overnight rejuvenation.
fields.ingredients: Aqua (Water), Glycerin, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate, PEG-100 Stearate, Sodium Hyaluronate, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Panthenol, Shea Butter (Butyrospermum Parkii), Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Allantoin, Xanthan Gum, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin
fields.usage: Cleanse your face thoroughly and pat dry.Apply a pea-sized amount of the night cream to the face and neck.Use every evening as the final step of your skincare routine.

fields.name: Replenishing Night Moisturizer
fields.description: A rich cream that hydrates and restores skin overnight, leaving it soft, smooth, and revitalized.
fields.ingredients: Aqua (Water), Glycerin, Caprylic/Capric Triglyceride, Cetearyl Alcohol, Glyceryl Stearate, PEG-100 Stearate, Shea Butter (Butyrospermum Parkii), Sodium Hyaluronate, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Panthenol, Aloe Barbadensis Leaf Juice, Allantoin, Xanthan Gum, Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin
fields.usage: Apply a moderate amount to clean, dry skin in the evening. Gently massage onto the face and neck using upward circular motions until fully absorbed. Use nightly as the final step of your skincare routine for soft, smooth, and revitalized skin by morning.

fields.name: Reverence Aromatique Balm
fields.description: A nourishing balm that deeply hydrates the skin and revitalizes the complexion, leaving it smooth.
fields.ingredients: Shea Butter, Cocoa Butter, Jojoba Oil, Sweet Almond Oil, Beeswax, Vitamin E (Tocopherol), Chamomile Extract, Essential Oils (optional)
fields.usage: Cleanse your skin thoroughly, take a small amount of the balm with your fingertips, gently massage onto dry areas or the entire face in circular motions, allow the balm to absorb fully, use daily, preferably at night, for maximum hydration and skin revitalization.

fields.name: Pure Micellar Cleansing Water
fields.description: Gently removes impurities and makeup, leaving skin clean, soft, and refreshed.
fields.ingredients: Water (Aqua), Glycerin, Coco-Glucoside, Decyl Glucoside, Aloe Vera Extract, Chamomile Extract, Cucumber Extract, Panthenol, Allantoin, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Phenoxyethanol, Ethylhexylglycerin
fields.usage: Apply a small amount to a cotton pad or fingertips, gently massage onto face to remove impurities and makeup, rinse with lukewarm water if needed, pat skin dry, use morning and evening for clean and refreshed skin.

fields.name: Extra Sensitive Calming Serum
fields.description: Strengthens the skinÆs barrier and leaves the complexion calm, comfortable, and balanced.
fields.ingredients: Ceramides, Niacinamide (Vitamin B3), Glycerin, Squalane, Panthenol, Shea Butter, Allantoin, Cholesterol, Phytosphingosine, Tocopherol (Vitamin E), Sodium Hyaluronate
fields.usage: Apply a small amount to clean skin, gently massage until fully absorbed, focus on areas prone to dryness or irritation, use daily, morning and evening, for a calm, balanced, and strengthened skin barrier.

fields.name: Brightening dark spot serum
fields.description: Brightens and hydrates skin while reducing dark spots naturally. Gentle, soothing, and glowing formula with raspberry, aloe vera, and hyaluronic acid.
fields.ingredients: Distilled water ,aloe vera gel,raspberry powder , hyaluronic acid ,rosehip oil,
fields.usage: Apply 2û3 drops to dark spots or the entire face once daily, gradually increasing to morning and evening if your skin tolerates it. Always follow with SPF during the day to protect results.
